Package com.palmergames.bukkit.towny.object

Interface Savable

All Known Implementing Classes:
District, Government, Jail, Nation, ObjectGroup, PlotGroup, Resident, Town, TownBlock, TownyObject, TownyWorld
public interface Savable
Basic interface that depicts whether an object has a specified save method. Most, if not all, save methods will redirect to a specific method in TownyDataSource. Using the save() method is preferred to future proof against database class changes.
